title: Keith Urban Grabs Nicole Kidman's Butt on the Oscars Red Carpet
text:
Nicole Kidman and Keith Urban at the 2017 Oscars Keith Urban Grabs Nicole Kidman's Butt on the Oscars Red Carpet February 26, 2017 Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 Keith Urban Grabs Nicole Kidman's Butt on the Oscars Red Carpet 
Nicole Kidman and Keith Urban never disappoint when it comes to walking a red carpet together , and things were no different at the Oscars on Sunday night. The two, who have been married since 2006 , seemed like newlyweds when they showed PDA while posing for photos together at the Dolby Theatre. In addition to holding hands and exchanging some loving glances, Keith also grabbed his wife's butt. We can't with these two. So cute.
